{"type": "article", "id": 7268, "title": "Robert Kolenik 水族馆灶台", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-11T07:22:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234251vUo5cgemhHs7xRGO.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t荷兰设计师 Robert Kolenik 推出的这款厨房设计把厨房和水族馆结合在了一起，这个呈 “ L” 形状的水族箱上面铺设了一层白色的桌台，设置灶台，洗碗池等基本设施，同时水箱的多余空间被用作了收纳柜。而且顶部的桌台可以通过一个桌面按钮自由升降。这是<a href=\"http://www.kolenik.com/\" target=\"_blank\">他们的官网</a>，可以提供预订服务。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234249hOHb3VEfqUStJ745.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.48240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234249nkeAOGiUNlLhXfF9.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.51296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234250tY3huKwRrzQEVqsa.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.45\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}